    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, I don't want to be here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I cannot win with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and, and they went on bicycles to call help.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And how long will it take?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was-- this was the story of-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with, with the-- with the-- with the what do you call it--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The [POLISH] commander, the [INAUDIBLE] commander.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[POLISH] was the was the lagerfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[POLISH] from, from, from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] This was-- this was the already end of the year.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "End of the year-- end of the year was-- was-- this was after the [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were-- went to clean up again to [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All of a sudden, it was-- we heard in the camp that there was-- there is evacuation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
